https://www.jpost.com/Israel-News/Maryland-reports-third-case-of-measles-587229


The Maryland Department of Health says it confirmed a 3rd measles case in a Maryland resident, Reuters reported on Wednesday [17 Apr 2019].

Since March [2019], more than 15 people in Oakland County, Michigan, were confirmed as suffering from measles following a person visiting the USA from Israel.

New York's Metropolitan Transportation Authority is currently investigating a complaint by a Haredi Orthodox man, who alleges that a bus driver refused to stop for him at a Brooklyn bus stop over the current measles outbreak.

